@node "stor"
@title "FRaNKy's Reset V 1.1 - The Story Off"
                                 THE STORY OFF
                                ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
TFX asked me to do a reset door.. It was something he needed for his BBS
and I made it quite quickly...

Later on he wanted a reason why the bbs was resetted and also the ability
to lock the door, wich I both added.

@endnode
@node "lock"
@title "Locking and Unlocking the door"
                            LOCKING & UNLOCKING
                           ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ

To lock and unlock the door, start the Rexx-Script LOCK.REXX by
typing in shell

'RX Doors:PTL/Reset/Lock.Rexx'

The program will detect if the door is locked or not and will then ask
you if you want to Lock/Unlock the door.

WARING !
--------

DO *NOT* START THIS DOOR FROM WITHIN AMI-EXPRESS !

@endnode
