@node "memb"
@title "Purple Turtle Is Always Looking For New Members"
                           LOOKING FOR NEW MEMBERS
                          ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
  If you think you are the right guy (girl) for a cool group and you can do
  some Coding (ASM-C-Arexx-...), Music, Graphics, Trading, Swapping or have
      a BBS, then contact the Purple Turtle Leaders or Division Leaders
                   for a certain reply on one of our HQ's.

   If you want to join with your BBS, we do not ask any donations for your
    membership (in another way : it's free !).  BBS's outside Belgium are
                              extremely welcome...

